name: M E A T S U I T
description:
[SIMULATANEON SERIES #003]

M E A T S U I T

Deep within the naturally selected features of earthly beasts lies the hidden circuitry of out-of-time perception and mathematical veil-peeping. An expertly crafted space-traveling piece of machinery. Its user manual can be heard amongst the bloodstream rumble of covered ears.

SIMULATANEON is a 2017 hypersigil and a conceptual prison break map for the upcoming matrix system update. The sigils that were borrowed for this series reveal only part of a bigger tapestry.
